      "content": "it doesnt feel like something i can just \"heal\" from though. i was a certain person. i had weight, i had influence. now i'm just a joke to everyone who used to respect me. how do you even find \"purpose\" when your entire identity was tied to the thing that's now gone? it feels like there is no version of me that exists without that career.",
